               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus” (fols. 5ra-118rb) &#xD; I-1)
                     Introduction (fols. 5ra-10rc)&#xD; - On John the Evangelist as the author of
                     the book; on the creation and the fall of the angels (fols. 5ra-7vb)&#xD; -
                     Story of the family of Adam (fols. 7vb-10rc)&#xD; I-2) Taʾāmra ʾIyasus
                     “Miracles of Jesus”: 41 (?) miracles (fols. 10rc-118rb)&#xD; &#xD;
                     Colophon.</summary>
